  "notes": [
    "This paper presents a computational method for identifying genetic interventions in cancer cells using integrated metabolic and regulatory networks",
    "The gMIS approach extends beyond traditional synthetic lethality to include synthetic dosage lethality and tumor suppressor gene complexes",
    "Validation was performed using DepMap data and other established databases"
